OL,3,CNational Crime Agency to investigate
OL,4,Cclaims police involved in Rotherham
OL,5,Cabuse
OL,7,FAn investigation into allegations
OL,8,Fpolice officers took part in
OL,9,Fhistorical sexual abuse in Rotherham
OL,10,Fis to be taken over by the National
OL,11,FCrime Agency.
OL,13,FLast month, survivors of sexual
OL,14,Fexploitation in the town said they had
OL,15,F"no faith" in the South Yorkshire
OL,16,FPolice investigation into its former
OL,17,Fofficers in relation to a number of
OL,18,Fallegations.
OL,20,FThree former police officers have so
OL,21,Ffar been arrested.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G1/10
