OL,5,Cabuse
OL,7,FThe Police watchdog, Independent
OL,8,FOffice for Police Conduct (IOPC),
OL,9,Fconfirmed it will now be carried out
OL,10,Fby the NCA.
OL,12,FHowever, the IOPC said it was
OL,13,Fresponding to "concerns about SYP's
OL,14,Finvolvement and a perception of a
OL,15,Fconflict of interest".
OL,17,FIt said it was a joint decision with
OL,18,Fthe force to ask the NCA to take over
OL,19,Fand that it remains satisfied there
OL,20,Fwas no conflict of interest.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G2/10
