OL,7,FThe law firm Switalskis, which
OL,8,Frepresents survivors of abuse in
OL,9,FRotherham, welcomed the move as a
OL,10,F"step in the right direction" but said
OL,11,Ftheir clients remained concerned over
OL,12,Fthe continued involvement of the IOPC.
OL,14,FSix women, who were sexually exploited
OL,15,Fby gangs in Rotherham as children,
OL,16,Fclaim they were also abused by local
OL,17,Fpolice officers.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G3/10
