OL,5,Cabuse
OL,7,FOne girl was raped from the age of 12
OL,8,Fin a marked police car and the officer
OL,9,Fthreatened to hand her back to the
OL,10,Fgroomers if she did not do as he said.
OL,12,FLast month, victims' lawyers said it
OL,13,Fhad hoped that alleged abuse by
OL,14,Fofficers would have been unearthed
OL,15,Ffollowing Operation Linden - a long-
OL,16,Frunning, IOPC investigation into how
OL,17,Fpolice responded to child sexual abuse
OL,18,Fin Rotherham between 1997 and 2013.
OL,20,FThey said South Yorkshire Police
OL,21,F"resisted" their requests.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G4/10
