OL,3,CNational Crime Agency to investigate
OL,4,Cclaims police involved in Rotherham
OL,5,Cabuse
OL,7,F"For years South Yorkshire Police
OL,8,Fresisted our requests for an
OL,9,Finvestigation into the alleged
OL,10,Fcriminality of police officers,
OL,11,Fdespite us providing them with the
OL,12,Faccounts of survivors."
OL,14,FIn 2022, Operation Linden concluded
OL,15,Fthat the force fundamentally failed in
OL,16,Fits duty to protect vulnerable
OL,17,Fchildren and young people during the
OL,18,Fperiod under investigation.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G5/10
