OL,7,FIOPC director Emily Barry said she
OL,8,Fwants to make sure people feel able to
OL,9,Fcome forward with complaints.
OL,11,F"We recognise the concerns that have
OL,12,Fbeen raised by some about SYP
OL,13,Finvestigating serious complaints
OL,14,Frelating to former SYP officers and we
OL,15,Fwant to ensure that any victim-
OL,16,Fsurvivors feel able to come forward
OL,17,Fwith complaints about former SYP
OL,18,Fofficers."
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G6/10
