OL,7,FThe NCA said the investigation will be
OL,8,Fcarried out by officers from Operation
OL,9,FStovewood - the agency's extensive
OL,10,Fdecade-long investigation into child
OL,11,Fsexual exploitation in Rotherham
OL,12,Fbetween 1997 and 2013.
OL,14,FIt has identified more than 1,100
OL,15,Fchildren involved in the exploitation
OL,16,Fin Rotherham, resulting in the
OL,17,Fconviction of 47 offenders who have so
OL,18,Ffar received prison sentences
OL,19,Ftotalling more than 1,300 years,
OL,20,Fincluding concurrent sentences.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G7/10
