OL,7,FAssistant Chief Constable, Hayley
OL,8,FBarnett, said: "Today's force,
OL,9,Fincluding the officers and staff who
OL,10,Fhave been directly involved in this
OL,11,Finvestigation, are appalled by the
OL,12,Fnature of the allegations which have
OL,13,Fcome to light.
