OL,7,F"However, we are acutely aware that
OL,8,Fwhile our culture, our processes and
OL,9,Four workforce here at SYP have
OL,10,Ftransformed in the decades since the
OL,11,Ffailings in Rotherham, the harm
OL,12,Fsuffered by the victim survivors
OL,13,Fremains their reality every single
OL,14,Fday."
